investigation.title: Proteomics and Transcriptomics analysis of Arabidopsis Seedlings in Microgravity
investigation.description: On Earth plants are constantly exposed to a gravitational field of 1G. Gravity affects a plant in every step of its development.

project.title: Proteomics analysis of Arabidopsis seedlings in microgravity
